OL,6,FRoberta Batchelor was working as a
OL,7,Fward manager for the University
OL,8,FHospitals Birmingham NHS Foundation
OL,9,FTrust when she posted on Facebook in
OL,10,FAugust 2024 a series of images
OL,11,Fincluding a boat filled with people
OL,12,Farriving at a beach captioned "these
OL,13,Fgive nothing and get everything" and a
OL,14,Fhomeless veteran with the caption
OL,15,F"these give everything and get
OL,16,Fnothing".
