OL,6,FThe Nursing and Midwifery Council
OL,7,F(NMC) said she also posted a picture
OL,8,Fof a child being chased by men, one
OL,9,Fwielding a knife, captioned "Next time
OL,10,Fwhen you pay your taxes, remember some
OL,11,Fof your money goes for the "Protection
OL,12,Fof Mosques."
OL,14,FA further image showed a highlighted
OL,15,Fsection of the book of Deuteronomy
OL,16,Fstating "Foreigners who live in your
OL,17,Fland will gain more and more power,
OL,18,Fwhile you gradually lose yours.
