OL,6,F"They will have money to lend you, but
OL,7,Fyou will have none to lend them. In
OL,8,Fthe end they will be your rulers."
OL,10,FBatchelor also posted split image
OL,11,Fshowing a security inspection
OL,12,Fcaptioned "YOU AT THE AIRPORT" and a
OL,13,Fman departing from a boat captioned
OL,14,F"MUHAMMAD AT DOVER".
OL,16,FThe Trust was alerted to her posts in
OL,17,FAugust 2024 after receiving a
OL,18,Fcomplaint from a member of the public
OL,19,Fraising concerns about posts on her
OL,20,Fpublic Facebook account, claiming that
OL,21,Fthe posts were racially abusive.
