OL,6,FShe worked her way up from a cleaner
OL,7,Fto managing a ward, winning a Pride of
OL,8,FNursing award in 2015.
OL,10,FThe NMC panel considered the order to
OL,11,Fstrike off as "necessary to protect
OL,12,Fthe public and to mark the seriousness
OL,13,Fof Mrs Batchelor's misconduct and
OL,14,Funderpin the importance of maintaining
OL,15,Fpublic confidence in the profession,
OL,16,Fand send to the public and the
OL,17,Fprofession a clear message about the
OL,18,Fstandard of behaviour required of a
OL,19,Fregistered nurse".
